These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, onion, grapes, tomato
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, amaryllis, zinnia, tulip
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, scientific, zombie, animation
1. the person eating onion is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person eating avocado##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
6. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person eating onion##1
7. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food   | avocado    | grapes      | onion      | tomato    |
| Flower   | tulip | daisy | amaryllis | zinnia |
| Movie-Genre     | scientific    | animation       | zombie     | satire     |

