.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, iced-tea, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, golf, surfing, rowing
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, japanese, german, indonesian
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the german is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the indonesian is on the far left##1
5. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
6. the brazilian is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage          | almond-milk     | lemonade     | mirinda       | iced-tea    |
| Sport         | golf | surfing   | swimming | rowing |
| Nationality   | indonesian    | german | japanese    | brazilian        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
City: miami, boston, new-york, hamburg
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, dunhill, bolivar, vegafina
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, blue, purple, grey
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
3. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
4. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
7. the person traveling to miami is on the far left##1
8. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| City      | miami | boston  | new-york    | hamburg |
| Cigar   | bolivar   | vegafina  | old-henry  | dunhill    |
| Color         | blue    | grey | apricot | purple  |

