.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, doctor, photographer, software-developer
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, fuchsia, mauve, brown
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, house, funk, r&b
1. the fan of house is between the person who likes fuchsia and the pilot##2
2. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
3. the fan of funk is on the right of the photographer##1
4. the photographer is on the far left##1
5. the fan of blues is the software-developer##1
6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the fan of house##1
7. the software-developer is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
8. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the doctor##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job          | photographer   | pilot     | doctor | software-developer |
| Color   | mauve | brown | lilac   | fuchsia     |
| Music-Genre           | r&b | funk      | house     | blues       |

