.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, train, ship, subway
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, chestnut, light-blue, white
City: new-york, edinburgh, london, miami
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
3. the person who likes light-blue is the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person who likes ivory is between the person driving the ship and the person driving the train##2
5. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes white##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
8. the person driving the ship is the person traveling to london##1
9. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Transport          | ship      | subway | train      | snowmobile |
| Color           | chestnut | ivory | white | light-blue   |
| City   | london    | miami   | edinburgh     | new-york   |

