.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, february, january, march
4 different pets are kept: pony, turtle, dog, frog
There 4 different types of food: cherry, banana, grapes, cucumber
1. the person eating banana is the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person eating grapes is the owner of the frog##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
5. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Birthday           | july    | february   | january | march |
| Pet   | pony     | dog   | frog         | turtle        |
| Food         | banana | cherry | grapes         | cucumber       |

