.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up, almond-milk, milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, skateboarding, golf
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, september, november
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
11. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage         | almond-milk    | mirinda  | 7up | milk   |
| Sport           | golf | cycling   | skateboarding    | basketball |
| Birthday   | november      | september | july | june  |

