2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
4. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
8. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
