.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, november, february, december
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, rowing, volleyball, swimming
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, video-games, filmmaking, cooking
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday      | november    | february            | december     | april      |
| Sport           | weightlifting    | swimming | volleyball     | rowing |
| Hobby   | collecting | filmmaking    | video-games | cooking    |

