.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, snowboarding, weightlifting, golf
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, techno, folk, trance
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, roller, taxi, boat
1. the fan of folk is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
5. the fan of trance is the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
7. the fan of techno is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Sport          | snowboarding   | weightlifting | rugby | golf |
| Music-Genre   | folk   | techno     | pop      | trance  |
| Transport   | scooter | roller   | taxi    | boat   |

