4. the craftsman house is on the right of the modern house##1
5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
6. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
7. the person eating banana is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
8. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
