.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-12::.
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, pakistani, argentine, polish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bolivar, ritmeester, baccarat
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, white, fuchsia, aquamarine
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the person who likes white is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
4. the turkish is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
5. the turkish is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
6. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person who likes white and the pakistani##2
7. the turkish is the bolivar-smoker##1
8. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality    | turkish   | argentine   | pakistani    | polish |
| Cigar         | bolivar | ritmeester    | aristoff      | baccarat |
| Color   | white      | aquamarine | fuchsia | blood-red   |

