4. the tower house is between the colonial house and the farmhouse house##2
5. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
8. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
